(49, 17, 'content', '\r\n				<p style=\"font-size:16px; line-height: 2\"></p><p><strong>» LEED consultancy service</strong> is provided to clients seeking the LEED certification for their buildings in accordance with the regulations of the US Green Building Council (USGBC).<br>\r\nECB’s LEED consultancy services span along the project’s different stages in adherence with the relative codes and regulation in order to achieve the client’s requirements in a timely fashion.</p>\r\n<p><strong>»</strong> <strong>Our LEED consultancy services</strong> encompass the following:</p>\r\n<p>★ General LEED consultancy.<br>\r\n★ LEED consultancy during construction.<br>\r\n★ LEED commissioning.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n			'),
