(55, 18, 'content', '\r\n				<p style=\"font-size:16px; line-height: 2\"></p><p><strong>»</strong> For over 20 years, <strong>ECB</strong> has served the process of valuing real estate properties for many clients, Banks and Real estate financing companies.</p>\r\n<p><strong>»</strong> The services include:</p>\r\n<p>★ Adequate description of the property.<br>\r\n★ Market data, and other factual data studies including risk assessment, mitigation, and contingency plans of actions.<br>\r\n★ The latitude of the reasoning in determining the value opinion.<br>\r\n★ A final value opinion.</p>\r\n<p></p>'),
