(61, 19, 'content', '\r\n				<p style=\"font-size:16px; line-height: 2\"></p><p><strong>»</strong> Our extensive experience in the field of construction allows us to carry out a thorough feasibility study for our clients.</p>\r\n<p><strong>»</strong> The feasibility studies are undertaken by highly qualified and experienced professionals who carry out the following steps in order to provide a complete, reliable, and informative feasibility report:</p>\r\n<p>★ Needs identification &amp; analysis.<br>\r\n★ Options &amp; alternatives analysis.<br>\r\n★ Due diligence for each option.<br>\r\n★ Financial analysis.<br>\r\n★ Construct-ability analysis.</p>\r\n<p></p>'),
